<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="salute-v">salute <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sə'luːt/    美 /sə'luːt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(向...) 打招呼；(向...) 行礼：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Those in the cars waved and we saluted them back. 
车上的人向我们挥手，我们向他们回礼。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They salute the flag every day at school. 
在学校里他们每天都向国旗行礼。</p></div></div>